*{{cite book | author=Andrew Smith | title=In Search of the Men Who Fell to Earth: Moondust | publisher=Bloomsbury | year=2005 | id=ISBN 978-0-7475-6368-6}}
* Thompson, Milton O. (1992) ''At The Edge Of Space: The X-15 Flight Program'', Smithsonian Institution Press, Washington and London. ISBN 978-1-56098-107-7
